==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lumberer
<hw>Lum"ber*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One employed in
lumbering, cutting, and getting logs from the forest for lumber; a
lumberman.</def> <mark>[U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Lumberers</qex> have a notion that he (the woodpecker) is
harmful to timber.</q> <rj><qau>Lowell.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lumbering</ent>⟦br⟧
